nodes.text: Dark Times 16, also titled with the legacy numbering Republic 99, is the sixteenth issue of the Legends comic book series Star Wars: Dark Times. It was written by Randy Stradley, illustrated by Douglas Wheatley and Dan Jackson, and first published by Dark Horse Comics on April 14, 2010.

Former Jedi Dass Jennir has woven a tangled web of lies in his quest to topple two opposing gangs. Now, all the threads are about to break, and the gangs will tear the town apart in a war that may doom those Jennir sought to save—but not before they take their vengeance out on him!
